Installation Instructions

NOTE: The instructions are written to install from the file "c2e2-2.0.0.tar.gz" into the 
    directory "~/C2E2/". Please change these to the approriate file/directory if needed. 
    

1. Unzip the files into a local directory, such as ~/C2E2/
    
    tar -xvzf c2e2-2.0.0.tar.gz -C ~/C2E2/
    
2. Navigate to the that local directory and run installRequirements with superuser priveledges

    cd ~/C2E2/
    sudo ./installRequirements

3. Run C2E2!

    cd ~/C2E2/
    sudo ./runC2E2